<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<RelativeLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    tools:context=".peterbhau">

    <ScrollView
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="match_parent">
        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="match_parent"
            android:orientation="vertical">
            <LinearLayout
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="230dp"
                android:orientation="horizontal"
                android:background="#fcfcfc">

                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="190dp"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:orientation="vertical">

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="40dp"
                        android:paddingTop="7dp"
                        android:paddingLeft="13dp"

                        android:text="Shubham Gawali"
                        android:layout_marginTop="70dp"
                        android:textColor="@color/black"
                        android:textSize="20dp"
                        android:textStyle="bold" />
                    <LinearLayout
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="1dp"
                        android:background="#919191"></LinearLayout>
                    <TextView
                        android:layout_marginLeft="15dp"
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="50dp"
                        android:text="Network: 110000
Promotiond done: 109
Subscriber: 1M" />


                </LinearLayout>
                <LinearLayout

                    android:layout_width="190dp"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent">
                    <ImageView

                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:id="@+id/Girishimage"
                        android:layout_alignParentTop="true"
                        android:layout_centerHorizontal="true"
                        android:contentDescription="hello_world"
                        android:layout_marginTop="24dp" />

                    <de.hdodenhof.circleimageview.CircleImageView
                        android:id="@+id/Girishcircle"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_below="@+id/GirishimageView"
                        android:layout_centerHorizontal="true"
                        android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                        android:layout_marginBottom="25dp"
                        android:layout_marginLeft="40dp"
                        android:paddingRight="10dp"
                        android:src="@drawable/bakra2" />

                </LinearLayout>
            </LinearLayout>
            <LinearLayout
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="1dp"
                android:background="#919191">
            </LinearLayout>
            <LinearLayout
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:orientation="vertical">
                <TextView
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:text="Dave Vaughan B.Comm, DipFP, JP

I began working as an adviser 4 years ago after a long career in the Australian Special Forces in the 2nd Commando Regiment. I had multiple overseas tours including 2 to Afghanistan.

I commenced study acheiving a Diploma in Financial Planning, Bachelor degree in Commerce (Finance) and then attended the AMP Horizons Academy to earn my financial adviser status.

I worked at a practice in Sydney's south for 2 years in which time I was awarded the AMP 2015 NSW 'New adviser of the year'. I also completed a Self managed super fund accreditation and Mortgage broking certificate. I then embarked on a Masters in Financial Planning through UNSW which I am currently 50% of the way through.

I have recently started a new business with a long time friend and fellow soldier during my time in the Special Forces Commandos called Loudon and Vaughan Private Wealth where I am continuing on my journey as an adviser with work and education.

I love being an adviser as I value my personal relationships with my clients and a job where you make other peoples lives better is something you wake up to with enthusiasm. I had that previously with my military career, and have found a similar drive and job satisfaction with this career.

"
                    android:textStyle="bold"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"/>



            </LinearLayout>
            <LinearLayout
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:orientation="vertical"
                android:layout_marginBottom="50dp">

            </LinearLayout>






        </LinearLayout>
    </ScrollView>

    <LinearLayout
        android:id="@+id/gawali_apply"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="50dp"
        android:layout_alignParentBottom="true"
        android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
        android:layout_alignParentLeft="true"
        android:layout_gravity="bottom|center"
        android:background="#3d7ee5"
        android:orientation="horizontal"
        tools:layout_editor_absoluteX="0dp"
        tools:layout_editor_absoluteY="486dp">

        <TextView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="match_parent"
            android:gravity="center"
            android:text="Apply"
            android:textColor="@color/white"
            android:textSize="20dp" />

    </LinearLayout>


</RelativeLayout>